name: Tomato Go: Escape from Space Robot Warhol Hell
name_original: Tomato Go: Escape from Space Robot Warhol Hell
description:
Tomtato Go is a turn based puzzle game about a mutant tomato escaping from space robots commanded by Andy Space Android Warhol.

Features:

  • Puzzle with enemy patterns and portals.

Credits:
Iuval Goldansky
Romina Calvette
Georgine Herbig
Manuel Atienza
Pablo A. Falero

We couldn't finish the initial 5 levels in 36 hours, so here you have them!
